Subject: Secunia Research: Lotus Notes kvdocve.dll Path Processing Buffer
	Overflow

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 08/04/2008

      - Lotus Notes kvdocve.dll Path Processing Buffer Overflow -

====================================================================== 
